llent and you have a shopping mall adjacent to the hotel with supermarket, western fast food and different restaurants. There is subway station right in front. Sometimes take a cab at the hotel is a problem and I believe they have settled drivers. One day I had to wait more than 15 minutes to get a cab while some are passing by the hotel, the bellboy just nodded when I asked why I couldn’t that one of these. I recommend the hotel for those not expecting a luxury accommodation and seeking for good price, service and location.	
